Valentino Yuel (amụrụ n'abalị iri na abụọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1994) bụ onye South Sudan na-agba bọọlụ nke ikpeazụ ya gbara bọọlụ dị ka onye na-agba ọsọ maka Newcastle Jets na A-League
Yuel bịanyere aka na klọb ọhụrụ Western United tupu 2019 a na-akpọ A-League. Ọ hapụrụ klọb ahụ na ngwụcha oge 2019 na 1920.
Mgbe ọnwa 2.5 na-enweghị klọb, gụnyere oge nnwale, Yuel sonyeere Newcastle Jets na nkwekọrịta afọ abụọ.
Mgbe ọ na-emeghị ihe maka Western United na egwuregwu 9 maka klọb ahụ, Yuel lere anya igosi onwe ya na A-League na Newcastle Jets
Yuel malitere ike, na-agba goolu atọ n'egwuregwu atọ, agbanyeghị na Yuel nọgidere na-agba otu goolu n'egwú asatọ ka Newcastle Jets setịpụrụ ndekọ klọb nke ruru 6 n'usoro.
Na 8 June 2021, a mara ọkwa na Yuel anabatala oku na ndị otu mba South Sudan. O mere nke mbụ ya na 31 Jenụwarị 2022 na-agba naanị goolu na mmeri 2-1 na Jordan.
